  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluative pilot study for safety and feasibility with administration of autologous bone bone
      marrow derived mononuclear cells by endoventricular catheter into the normal border zone fo
      the ischemic lesion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
