  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Demonstration of safety and feasibility of BM-MNC treatment. Investigation of the suitability of endocardial left ventricular electromechanical mapping (LVEMM) with NOGA as endpoint for myocardial regeneration.</measure>
    <time_frame>12 months</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Collection of first evidence on the best type and time points for the determination of myocardial regeneration by NOGA and other parameters.</measure>
    <time_frame>12 months</time_frame>
  </secondary_outcome>
